SIGNATURE ------------------------------- Pursuant to the requirements of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, the Registrant has duly caused this report to be signed on its behalf by the undersigned thereunto duly authorized. Date: May 29, 2002 AMERICAN SCIENCE AND ENGINEERING, INC. By: /s/ Ralph S. Sheridan --------------------------------------- Ralph S. Sheridan President and Chief Executive Officer -3-
