Effective September 8, 2003, Anthony R. Fabiano was named President and Chief Executive Officer of American Science and Engineering, Inc., replacing interim President and Chief Executive Officer, Dr. Roger Heinisch.  A copy of the press release issued on August 26, 2003 regarding the appointment of Mr. Fabiano is filed as Exhibit 99.1.
 
