On September 29, 2004 American Science and Engineering, Inc., announced that the Company has initiated action to transfer the listing of its securities from the American Stock Exchange to the Nasdaq Stock Exchange.  A copy of the Press Release issued on September 29, 2004 regarding the listing transfer is filed as Exhibit Number 99.1
 
