ITEM 1.01. ENTRY INTO A MATERIAL DEFINITIVE AGREEMENT.
On October 14, 2004 American Science and Engineering, Inc., announced that the Company entered into a material definitive agreement. A copy of the Press Release issued on October 14, 2004 regarding the agreement is filed as Exhibit Number 99.1
 
