ITEM 1.01. ENTRY INTO A MATERIAL DEFINITIVE AGREEMENT.
On January 5, 2005 American Science and Engineering, Inc., announced that the Company entered into a material definitive agreement.  A copy of the Press Release issued on January 5, 2005 regarding the agreement is filed as Exhibit Number 99.1
ITEM 9. 01
