Item 2.02. RESULTS OF OPERATIONS AND FINANCIAL CONDITION.
On February 9, 2007, American Science and Engineering, Inc. issued a press release announcing financial results for the third quarter ended December 31, 2006. A copy of the Press Release issued on February 9, 2007 regarding those results is filed as Exhibit 99.1.
    The information furnished in this Form 8-K and the Exhibit attached hereto shall not be deemed "filed" for purposes of Section 18 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended, or otherwise subject to the liabilities of that section, nor shall such information be deemed incorporated by reference in any filing under the Securities Act of 1933, as amended, except as shall be expressly set forth by specific reference in such a filing.
