ENTRY INTO A MATERIAL DEFINITIVE AGREEMENT.
ITEM 1.01.
  
On February 8, 2007, the Company's Board of Director's approved a modification to the Change of Control and Termination for Convenience Program (the "CIC Program") for members of the executive staff changing the provision involving the amount of payment such executive will be eligible to receive in the event a designated executive is terminated in connection with a change of control event from one times base salary plus annual target bonus to two times base salary plus target bonus. The CIC Program was adopted by the Company in September 2005, and in all other respects will remain unchanged and in full force and effect.
 
