DEPARTURE OF DIRECTORS OR PRINCIPLE OFFICERS; ELECTION OF DIRECTORS;   APPOINTMENT OF PRINCIPAL OFFICERS.
 
On June 3, 2008 the Company announced the passing of General William E. Odom, the Chairman of its Board of Directors.  The Company also announced the appointment of current Board member Denis R. Brown to succeed General Odom as Chairman. The related Press Release is included as Exhibit 99.1 to this report.
 
