.  Borrower hereby ratifies, confirms and reaffirms, all and singular, the terms and disclosures contained in a certain Perfection Certificate dated as of August 11, 2003, between Borrower and Bank, and acknowledges, confirms and agrees the disclosures and information Borrower provided to Bank in the Perfection Certificate has not changed, as of the date hereof, except to the extent such disclosure is updated by the information contained in , attached hereto as a supplement to the Exhibit B previously delivered to the Bank.
