and inserting in lieu thereof the following:
 
"
2.2
                        
Overadvances
.  If, at any time Borrower's Unrestricted Cash, Cash Equivalents, and short-term investments maintained with Bank or Bank's Affiliates are less than Forty Million Dollars ($40,000,000.00) for a period of thirty (30) consecutive days, and the Credit Extensions under Sections 2.1.1, 2.1.2, 2.1.3 and 2.1.4 exceed the lesser of either (a) the Revolving Line or (b) the Borrowing Base, Borrower shall immediately pay to Bank in cash such excess."
 
