Cause
 
respect to the Company or any of its Affiliates, or (v) Executive's conviction of, or pleading guilty or no contest to, any felony or other crime involving moral turpitude, or (vi) a breach of any confidentiality/non-competition/ non-solicitation agreement. With respect to a breach of (i), (ii), or (iii), Executive shall be given 30 days, after written notice of such breach, to cure a breach to the reasonable satisfaction of the Company.
 
